OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781892673
OL,3,CMum of teenager who took her own life
OL,4,Cfights to 'break the stigma of suicide'
OL,6,FA mum has spoken of her 'shock', after
OL,7,Flosing her 13-year-old daughter to
OL,8,Fsuicide - and how she is now fighting
OL,9,Fto change the stigma around it.
OL,11,FEmily Grace Kelly, from the Isle of
OL,12,FMan, was described by her family as a
OL,13,F'beacon of kindness', but in October
OL,14,F2025, she took her own life.
OL,16,FHer mum Caroline described her as
OL,17,F"smart and beautiful", adding that she
OL,18,F"never thought Emily was feeling like
OL,19,Fthis".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
