FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781892673
OL,3,CMum of teenager who took her own life
OL,4,Cfights to 'break the stigma of suicide'
OL,6,F"We are very close, and this is why
OL,7,Fit's come as such a shock, because I
OL,8,Fdidn't see it coming," Caroline said.
OL,10,F"She'd jump into my bed and we'd talk
OL,11,Fabout my day, her day, she'd tell me
OL,12,Fthings about her friends and what's
OL,13,Fgoing on.
OL,15,F"It doesn't matter how old you are,
OL,16,Fwhat background you have, you can see
OL,17,Fsomeone smiling being happy like I
OL,18,Fdid, and you don't know what's going
OL,19,Fon or how they're feeling on the
OL,20,Finside... it doesn't always show."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781892673
OL,3,CMum of teenager who took her own life
OL,4,Cfights to 'break the stigma of suicide'
OL,6,FCaroline is now determined to raise
OL,7,Fawareness of mental health issues, and
OL,8,Fbreak the stigma surrounding suicide.
OL,10,FShe is set to take on the annual
OL,11,FParish Walk on 20 June, raising funds
OL,12,Ffor charities Ed Space and Isle Stand
OL,13,Fup to Suicide.
OL,15,F"I didn't understand mental health or
OL,16,Fanything like that, until it happened
OL,17,Fto me", she said. "I didn't know there
OL,18,Fwas charities out there, people out
OL,19,Fthere that want to help without
OL,20,Fjudgement.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1781892673
OL,3,CMum of teenager who took her own life
OL,4,Cfights to 'break the stigma of suicide'
OL,6,F"And it's taken me a long time to feel
OL,7,Fstrong enough to do this."
OL,9,FThe Parish Walk will see Caroline take
OL,10,Fon an 85-mile, 24-hour walking
OL,11,Fchallenge around the Island.
OL,13,FShe is set to start her challenge at
OL,14,F10.00am at the National Sports Centre
OL,15,Fin Douglas.
OL,17,FWalking from parish to parish with the
OL,18,Fultimate message: "It's ok not to be
OL,19,Fok, it's ok to ask for help. It's no
OL,20,Fembarrassing, it's not shameful, it's
OL,21,Fok."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
